  "texts": [
    "The healthcare community uses 5G services to fetch data from the cloud and transmit data to the cloud.",
    "Edge layerIoT devices at the sensing layer gather and evaluate patient data before triggering actions depending on the insights provided.",
    "In our instance, these insights are required in real-time; hence, edge computing is required.",
    "It will bring computation nearer to the IoT device, as well as data collecting and analytics, to a physically closer area.",
    "This reduces network latency since the round trip to the data center, and return is shorter."
  ],
